if you want to read faster.

56
00:04:40,200 --> 00:04:44,479
Or to think up funnier jokes
in social situations.

57
00:04:44,640 --> 00:04:46,597
She seems to like it.

58
00:04:46,760 --> 00:04:48,991
Tempting, isn' t it?

59
00:04:49,160 --> 00:04:51,550
But just take a look
